{"id": "1510537598051942520", "channel_id": "1510243169336430644", "type": 19, "author_id": "702430527994724432", "author_name": "ice3564", "author_bot": false, "content": "If you have Thais in the team, no need to OE Gmurphy.  If not, having OE is recommended for carry. \n\n\nAlternative, if you play e3Gmurphy with Saya.\n\nYou can :\n> holding Gmurphy 3 cost\n> use it\n> use Saya Exalt and select Gmurphy\n> use Gmurphy exclusive posses [which will trigger twice due to Saya exalt] \n> draw 2 copies of 3 cost to use again. \n\nThat combo should be more than enough for most non-endgame  content.", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T06:57:07.807000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-31T07:03:55.367000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["410424004411785216"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1510391231069294832", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510243169336430644", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Saya no Uta : Team Guide", "forum_channel_id": "1304022827824844842", "thread_tags": ["1304022913686437930", "1304022948000043028"]}
